Class Link

java.lang.Object
com.powerbi.api.model.Link
@Entity public class Link extends Object
Represents a Link entity in the system. A link is associated with a user and contains metadata such as title, description, and URL. Includes fields for the link's ID, URL, title, description, and creation date. This entity is mapped to a database table using JPA annotations.
